<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Exercise 5 - Alignment & Ordering</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container my-5">
        <h2>5. Alignment & Reordering</h2>
        <h4 class="mt-4 text-muted">Exercise 5.1: Centered Flex Layout</h4>
        <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center bg-light border rounded" style="height: 150px;">
            <div class="col-4 text-center bg-warning p-3 rounded">
                Perfectly Centered Box
            </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="mt-4 text-muted">Exercise 5.2: Column Reordering</h4>
        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                <div class="p-3 bg-primary text-white rounded">
                    Box A (Written 1st in HTML Code, Appears 2nd on Desktop)
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <div class="p-3 bg-danger text-white rounded">
                    Box B (Written 2nd in HTML Code, Appears 1st on Desktop)
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>